es_paneerstuffedpeppers_90032","title":"Paneer-stuffed peppers","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"30 mins to 1 hour","cookingMins":60,"totalMins":90},"serves":"Serves 4-8","image":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/food/ic/food_16x9_448/recipes/paneerstuffedpeppers_90032_16x9.jpg","isVegetarian":true,"recommendations":0}
