ured, rather than a smooth puree. Taste and add more salt, pepper or lemon juice as needed. Place into a bowl and finish with a few fine gratings of lemon zest. ","To serve, spoon the hotpot into warmed bowls and top with the sprout top pesto. "],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_parsnip_sprout_and_73857","title":"Parsnip, sprout and chestnut hotpot with cider and sprout top pesto","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"30 mins to 1 hour","cookingMins":60,"totalMins":90},"serves":"Serves 4","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":true,"recommendations":0}
