er sauce over the pasta, scatter the pea shoots over and serve immediately."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_pea_mint_and_ricotta_06456","title":"Pea, mint and ricotta ravioli with a pancetta butter","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"less than 10 mins","cookingMins":10,"totalMins":40},"serves":"Serves 2","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
