lid. Continue to simmer the stew and dumplings for 8-10 minutes, or until the meat and vegetables are tender, the sauce has thickened and the dumplings are cooked through."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_pepperpotstewwithspi_91703","title":"Pepperpot stew with spillers dumplings","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"1 to 2 hours","cookingMins":120,"totalMins":150},"serves":"Serves 8","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
